This is a quick port of Anne van Kesteren's XML5 project[1] from Python to
Ruby.  The version of the source that was ported is captured in the lib.py
directory, and the Ruby source retains much of the original Python structure.
The tests provided pass on both Ruby 1.8.7 and 1.9.2.

[1] http://code.google.com/p/xml5/
